{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "塞西娅 第2话 延续可能性",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "“起始之人”的复活\\n让世界踏上了毁灭的绝路。\\n邪恶的魔力笼罩整个世界，\\n导致天地异变和魔兽狂暴化……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "一旦发生这种情况，人们为寻求安稳\\n而四处流浪也是必然的结果。\\n圣都格拉姆斯就是这些人为了\\n求得安宁而聚集的其中一个地点。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "人多的地方物资和情报也很丰富……\\n就算是为了熬过即将到来的战争，\\n在格拉姆斯补充战斗力和收集情报\\n也是不可或缺的首要任务。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "抱有这种想法的不光是我们，\\n跟我们走散的尤蒂尔\\n他们也一定如此。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "所以为了与他们会合，\\n我们马不停蹄地\\n前往格拉姆斯。然而……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "刚才似乎是最后一个了……\\n你可以出来了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年",
            "context": "谢谢你们从魔兽手中\\n救了我！\\n大恩大德没齿难忘！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "不客气，相遇也是一种缘分，\\n你不必放在心上。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我们耽误了不少时间……\\n不快点赶路的话就没办法\\n在日落之前到达目的地了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "是啊，我们快走吧。\\n得尽快追上哥哥他们……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年",
            "context": "那、那个！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年",
            "context": "我知道自己刚得救\\n就又劳烦你们非常自私，\\n但是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年",
            "context": "求求你们了！\\n我的家人还在村子里，\\n你们能不能救救他们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "跟我们说说详细情况吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年",
            "context": "村子被狂暴化的魔兽袭击了。\\n可是我所在的村子里并没有\\n足以对抗魔兽的人或是武器……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "所以说……走投无路的你们\\n就采取了去别的村子\\n或镇上求助的最终手段？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年",
            "context": "是的……我们好不容易从魔兽手里\\n逃出来活到现在，要是没遇到你们，\\n我现在还不知道……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年",
            "context": "凭你们的实力，一定能和村子里\\n出现的魔兽抗衡。求求你们了！\\n救救我的村子还有家人吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你的村子在哪里？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年",
            "context": "朝西南方向穿过这片森林，\\n出去后沿着附近的河前进，\\n差不多半天就能到。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "（西南的话就是格拉姆斯的反方向啊。\\n去的时候半天，来回要一天……\\n现在时间紧迫，耽搁不起……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我们出发吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "唔！？塞西娅，\\n你知道自己在说什么吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "既然眼前有人在求救，\\n我们就不能坐视不管。\\n哥哥他一定也会这么说的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "好吧……既然你都这么说了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年",
            "context": "谢、谢谢你们！\\n啊啊，这一定是女神的旨意。\\n感谢女神，也感谢你们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "真不知道客气呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "敌人的数量没有多少。\\n我们兵分两路逐个击破比较好。\\n塞西娅，你能搞定吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "嗯，我已经准备就绪。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "那我们就准备上吧。\\n预备……开始！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "发现首领！时间紧迫，\\n我们速战速决吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "呃！？糟了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你没事吧，伊莉雅？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你的支援太及时了！\\n果然有什么都不如\\n有个好搭档呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "只是我的刀法\\n还不及莫尔提斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "哪里，你也很厉害哦。\\n只要你在我身边，\\n我就觉得自己战无不胜！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "太好了！这下村子\\n也暂时安全了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "嗯，是啊……\\n这样就好……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "伊莉雅……\\n你是不是在后悔……\\n不该为了救人而绕远路？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "也不能……算是后悔。\\n我不觉得做错了。\\n我们这么做应该是对的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "不过有一个念头一闪而过——\\n如今世上正在遭受\\n相同磨难的人有很多吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "那么我们只救眼前这些人\\n又有什么意义呢？我们是不是\\n应该更顾全大局才对？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "虽然……我并没有后悔……\\n算了，抱歉。\\n我好像有点急躁了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "伊莉雅……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "像这样为未知的事情而烦恼\\n恰恰证明了我们\\n还没有输给“起始之人”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "无论多么艰难，都要在烦恼的同时\\n坚信更好的可能性继续前进……\\n我们能做到的只有这些。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "这一定就是“起始之人”\\n所期盼的对抗世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "原来如此……你说得没错。\\n呵呵，不愧是女神的巫女大人，\\n说的话特别有内涵。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "别开我玩笑了。\\n你可不就是货真价实的\\n女神大人嘛。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "二人",
            "context": "噗……啊哈哈哈哈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "哈～谢谢你，塞西娅。\\n多亏了你，我心里畅快多了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "看不清方向的未来\\n似乎让我有点焦虑，\\n导致我的视野变得狭隘。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "无论何时，我们都依然拥有\\n名为希望的可能性……不相信它，\\n今后是无法继续战斗的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "要是怀疑可能性、\\n逃避应当履行的正义，\\n那才是输给了“起始之人”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "没错，我也是这么想的。\\n为了打败“起始之人”，就相信\\n当下的可能性，把它延续下去吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "相信可能性并延续下去吗……\\n不错！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "好，那我们的第一步\\n就是朝着目的地出发。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年的声音",
            "context": "请等一下！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年",
            "context": "你们这就要走了吗？\\n现在可还是深夜呢！？而且我们\\n还没来得及感谢你们的搭救……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "抱歉，我们得尽快\\n赶去格拉姆斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100054_01_01_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年",
            "context": "格拉姆斯……\\n既然如此我有个主意！",
